{"page_id":"106","title":"Ordering Frequently Asked Questions | BosterBio","identifier":"faqs","content_heading":"Ordering Frequently Asked Questions","update_time":"2024-06-12 01:02:59","content":"                                         <section class=\"mb-6 text-center hero-section\" style=\"background-image: url(/media/images/design-guide/waves-hero-image-1.png);\">\n        <div class=\"dark-overlap\">\n          <h1 class=\"mb-2\">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"mb-5 topic-heading-section\">\n<h2 class=\"topic-heading text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold typography-josefin-sans mb-3\">Featured question</h2>\n<p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">Q: How to view my orders' status and track my shipments?</p><p class=\"text-grey text-center w-75 mx-auto mb-5 font-medium\">A: go to <a href=\"/my-orders\" target=\"_blank\">bosterbio.com/my-orders</a></p>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"><div style=\"position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.loom.com/embed/31ca0b6aa4814f77b21a913ca00da083\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;\"></iframe></div></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\"></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"mb-6 accordion-section\">\n    <h2 class=\"topic-heading text-orange text-center font-larger text-uppercase font-weight-bold typography-josefin-sans mb-3\">FAQs</h2>\n    <div class=\"container\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/FAQPage\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n            <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordion-faq\">\n            <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem1\">Q1. What is Boster's Quality Policy?</a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem1\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can find more information on the Boster Quality Guarantee  <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/boster-guarantee\">here</a> or contact sup<span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"d3a3bca1a793b1bca0a7b6a1b1babcfdb0bcbe\">[email protected]</span> \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem2\">Q2. How do I contact the Customer Service / Sales team?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem2\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                        A:\n                            <ul>\n                            <li> For Orders: <span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"bcd3ced8d9cecffcded3cfc8d9ceded5d392dfd3d1\">[email protected]</span> </li>\n                            <li> For Customer/Technical Support: <span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"b2c1c7c2c2ddc0c6f2d0ddc1c6d7c0d0dbdd9cd1dddf\">[email protected]</span> </li>\n                            <li> Phone: (888) 466-3604 </li>\n                            <li> Live Chat: Click the floating action button on the bottom right of this page for live chat </li>\n                            </ul>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem3\">Q3. What is the intended use of the products?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem3\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Research Use Only (RUO)\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem4\">Q4. Do you offer Free samples/Trial Sizes? \n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem4\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: We do not offer free samples. But, you can choose a free sample or secondary antibody with every purchase of a standard-sized antibody. If the sample and antibody are not ordered concurrently, the sample can still be provided, but additional shipping and handling fees will apply.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem5\">Q5. Does Boster Bio make Custom Antibodies?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem5\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Boster offers both monoclonal and polyclonal antibody production services. For more information of this service, please refer to <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/services/custom-antibody-production-services\">this page</a> or contact <span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"9deee8ededf2efe9ddfff2eee9f8effff4f2b3fef2f0\">[email protected]</span>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem6\">Q6. Do you have any promotions going on currently?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem6\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Currently, we have a few continuous promotions going on. \n                            <ul>\n                            <li>Buy one primary antibody, get one free sample secondary antibody.</li>\n <li>Invite your friends to register and purchase, both of you can get coupons.</li>\n <li>Free validation of our product on other similar samples not labeled for testing. (number limited per month) </li>\n                            <li>Custom antibodies for non-standard model organisms at $600 each. </li>\n                            <li>Review us on biocompare and receive a $30 Amazon gift card.</li>\n <li>These promotions may update over time, go to https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/promotions to find the latest profits.</li>\n                        </ul>\n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem7\">Q7. How do I request a quote?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem7\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can contact customer support at <span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"9feceaefeff0edebdffdf0ecebfaedfdf6f0b1fcf0f2\">[email protected]</span> and ask for a quote by providing the product name, SKU, quantity, and shipping address..\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem8\">Q8. Can I have a pro-forma invoice?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem8\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Contact support at <span class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"dba8aeababb4a9af9bb9b4a8afbea9b9b2b4f5b8b4b6\">[email protected]</span> with the information required\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>  \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem9\">Q9. Is the product in stock?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem9\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: If the product ships next business day, then there is at least one in stock. If you need more information about products in stock. Please feel free to contact support.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem10\">Q10. How do I place an order?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem10\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: There are a few ways to do this:\n                            <ul>\n                                <li>Website: You can add the products you want into your cart and then check out.</li>\n                                <li> Offline ordering: You can call (888) 466-3604 to place your order. Just be prepared with the information required. </li>\n                                </ul>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem11\">Q11. What information do you require for my order?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem11\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Name, Email, Phone Number, Product SKU and quantity, Shipping/billing address, Purchase order/ or credit card information.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem12\">Q12. What type of payment methods are accepted\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem12\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Purchase Orders and Credit Cards\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem13\">Q13. How will I know if my order has been received by Boster?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem13\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You will receive an email confirmation after your purchase has been processed.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem14\">Q14. What are your shipping,handling, &amp; packaging charges?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem14\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: We have two shipping options:\n                            <ul>\n                                <li>FedEx overnight shipping - ELISA kits and Antibodies</li>\n                                <li>FedEx 3 day shipping - this option is for products that are not temperature sensitive </li>\n                            </ul>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem15\">Q15. How do I track my order?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem15\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can use your FedEx tracking number to track your order. If you require additional help, then please contact support.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem16\">Q16. I did not receive my order yet, how do I get information?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem16\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can contact support to get information on your orders status\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem17\">Q17. When do you ship?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem17\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: We ship at the end of the business day if the product is in stock. If the product is ordered on Friday with the one day shipping option, then the product will be shipped on Monday.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem18\">Q18. When can I expect to receive my order if I order directly from Boster.\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem18\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can expect to receive your order the next day if the product is in stock. If the product is not in stock, then you will receive it within 5-7 business days.\n                        \n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem19\">Q19. Which delivery company do you use?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem19\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: FedEx and UPS\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem20\">Q20. What do I do when the product I purchased did not produce expected results?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem20\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: You can contact support and provide the following information:\n                            <ul>\n                                <li>Product SKU and lot number</li>\n                                <li>What sample type did you detect?</li>\n                                <li>Protocol used and relevant data (OD values, etc)</li>\n                                <li>A detailed description of the problem (images if applicable) </li>\n                            </ul>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem21\">Q21. What other technical resources do you provide?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem21\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: We offer technical resources regarding ELISA, WB, IHC, and FACS on our website, we even have <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/wb-ihc-elisa-troubleshooting-handbooks\">Troubleshooting handbooks</a>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem22\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Q22. Do you have a distributor in my country?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem22\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\" style=\"\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: Please see our list of distributors <a href=\"https://SITE_ORIGIN_PLACEHOLDER/distributors\">here</a>\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem23\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Q23. My country is not on the list of distributors?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem23\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\" style=\"\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: If a distributor is not located in your country or region, you are able to direct order from Boster, however international shipping cost will apply.\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n                \n    \n                <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem24\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Q24. How do I claim a refund for my order?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem24\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\" style=\"\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: We are proud of the quality of our products. However, if the product does not perform well on the tested applications,we will provide a replacement or a refund once we confirm if it is a quality issue or not. Please refer to the technical support question above and our Boster Guarantee. Contact support@bosterbio.com at any step you need.\n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n  <div class=\"faq-wrapper\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"mainEntity\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Question\">\n                <h3 class=\"font-medium m-0 p-3 bg-lightgrey border-bottom\" itemprop=\"name\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"d-block collapsed\" \"=\"\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-target=\"#faqitem25\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Q25. I don’t have a Wash buffer (25X) in my Elisa kit. Can I use something else?\n                        </a></h3>\n                <div id=\"faqitem25\" class=\"collapse\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"acceptedAnswer\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Answer\" data-parent=\"#accordion-faq\" style=\"\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white\" itemprop=\"text\">\n                    A: PBS can substitute the Wash Buffer (25X).\n                        \n                </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    </section>\n       \n    \n"}